Package: txrevise
Title: Extend and revise transcript annotatons.
Version: 0.1
Authors.R: "Kaur Alasoo <kaur.alasoo@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: txrevise extends truncated transcript 
	annotations and splits them into independent transcript starts, 
	middle sections and transcript ends.
